INSERT INTO `comments` (`id`, `anime_id`, `user_id`, `comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 1, 1, 'To me, Youjo Senki was among the greatest anime I watched in 2017. I absolutely like the way Tanya was badass and was against the idea of being X being the impersonation of God', '2023-01-24 08:03:31', '2023-01-24 08:03:31'),
(2, 3, 2, 'I loved SAO because of Kirito. He always brought the hype and managed to keep me hooked to the series', '2023-01-24 08:24:39', '2023-01-24 08:24:39'),
(3, 1, 2, 'Tanya, the main actor is really amazing. The fact that she is a story for from grass to grace is so dope. Really looking towards what the directors have planned for season 2', '2023-01-24 08:25:56', '2023-01-24 08:25:56'),
(4, 1, 2, 'Season 2 is going to be mindblowing', '2023-01-24 08:26:42', '2023-01-24 08:26:42'),
(5, 6, 3, 'Bam\'s sacrifice to Rachael was so elegant and yet the girl was out to ill him all along. So sad', '2023-01-24 09:22:05', '2023-01-24 09:22:05'),
(6, 4, 3, 'I never ever for a second imagined that Mrs Makina was going to be evil in the long run. She was so supportive of Denji\'s ambitions', '2023-01-24 09:23:23', '2023-01-24 09:23:23'),
(7, 5, 3, 'I cried so hard when it finally dawned on me that Itachi was surely going to die. I liked how much he loved his brother and was willing to do anything for his survival', '2023-01-24 09:24:32', '2023-01-24 09:24:32'),
(8, 2, 3, 'Attack on Titan proved to me that there is no good side. Both sides had just been raised knowing that the other were demons sent to kill them. What they were doing was simply protecting their own', '2023-01-24 09:25:48', '2023-01-24 09:25:48'),
(9, 9, 4, 'Tokyo Ghoul was amazing. Personally I think it was better than Tokyo Ghoul Re', '2023-01-25 03:11:02', '2023-01-25 03:11:02'),
(10, 1, 4, 'The saga of Tanya the evil is among the best militarian anime I have seen so far', '2023-01-25 03:11:55', '2023-01-25 03:11:55'),
(11, 5, 4, 'Itachi was so good. OMG. My boy did not have to die LOL', '2023-01-25 03:12:43', '2023-01-25 03:12:43'),
(12, 6, 4, 'Bam was done dirty by Rachael. If I were him, I wouldn\'t try to go after her a second time', '2023-01-25 03:13:56', '2023-01-25 03:13:56'),
(13, 2, 4, 'Shiganshina District arc was the best arc in anime history for me', '2023-01-25 03:14:53', '2023-01-25 03:14:53'),
(14, 3, 4, 'Kirito was just a somewhat overpowered protagonist.', '2023-01-25 03:15:23', '2023-01-25 03:15:23'),
(15, 4, 4, 'OMG, Ms Makina is evil! The Plot thickens', '2023-01-25 03:15:54', '2023-01-25 03:15:54'),
(16, 7, 5, 'I liked Rezero so much. The romance between subaru and Ram was so electrifying', '2023-01-25 03:20:01', '2023-01-25 03:20:01'),
(17, 12, 4, 'Saitama is the ultimate GOAT. His power is just ridiculously amazing. Love the guy', '2023-01-25 09:11:26', '2023-01-25 09:11:26'),
(18, 12, 6, 'Best anime I have seen since Naruto', '2023-01-30 05:39:59', '2023-01-30 05:39:59'),
(19, 16, 6, 'I love how Light was almost able to get away with it', '2023-01-30 05:40:24', '2023-01-30 05:40:24'),
(20, 17, 6, 'The Sound effects of this Anime are crazy asf', '2023-01-30 05:40:45', '2023-01-30 05:40:45'),
(21, 7, 4, 'Rem and Ram are power house sisters. Their collaboration in battle is so amazing', '2023-01-30 05:48:07', '2023-01-30 05:48:07'),
(22, 14, 1, 'Jujutsu Kaisen was so dope. I loved the animation most of all. All hail MAPPA!', '2023-01-30 05:53:26', '2023-01-30 05:53:26'),
(23, 7, 1, 'Subaru Natski is the GOAT of Shonen Protagonists. Simply amazing', '2023-01-30 05:54:01', '2023-01-30 05:54:01'),
(24, 18, 7, 'Odd Taxi was amazing', '2023-01-30 05:59:23', '2023-01-30 05:59:23'),
(25, 13, 7, 'I like how Luffy is able to gear up to several more other levels', '2023-01-30 06:11:26', '2023-01-30 06:11:26'),
(26, 8, 7, 'Seyene Goku is the most powerfull anime character I am aware of', '2023-01-30 06:11:49', '2023-01-30 06:11:49'),
(27, 18, 7, 'Odd Taxi was simple and well curated at the same time', '2023-01-30 06:12:15', '2023-01-30 06:12:15'),
(28, 12, 7, 'One punch man is actually a showcase of when absolute power falls into the right hands', '2023-01-30 06:13:00', '2023-01-30 06:13:00'),
(29, 17, 8, 'Fire force was simply amazing in its visualz', '2023-01-30 06:23:46', '2023-01-30 06:23:46'),
(30, 31, 4, 'Code geas was legendary stuff my guys', '2023-01-30 10:04:19', '2023-01-30 10:04:19'),
(31, 32, 4, 'Loved the main actress and the star studded boy', '2023-01-30 10:04:42', '2023-01-30 10:04:42'),
(32, 30, 4, 'Steins gate was the epitome of evil and what happens when supernatural entities are let loose to roam free', '2023-01-30 10:05:12', '2023-01-30 10:05:12'),
(33, 21, 4, 'Dr Stone proved to me that tur love can solve anything', '2023-01-30 10:05:33', '2023-01-30 10:05:33'),
(34, 7, 4, 'Rem dying was the worst thing that happened to me LOL', '2023-01-30 10:05:55', '2023-01-30 10:05:55'),
(35, 29, 4, 'How no one realized that Saiki had pink hair still baffles me', '2023-01-30 10:06:23', '2023-01-30 10:06:23'),
(36, 31, 3, 'Lelouch proved to me that true justice can never exist', '2023-01-30 10:06:56', '2023-01-30 10:06:56'),
(37, 21, 3, 'Dr Stone was so amazing and I liked how the scientist guy was inventing stuff with basically nothing', '2023-01-30 10:07:43', '2023-01-30 10:07:43'),
(38, 32, 3, 'Made in Abyss was so well done but it receives so little credit', '2023-01-30 10:08:10', '2023-01-30 10:08:10'),
(39, 30, 3, 'Steins gate is similar to Blood Blockade Battlefront in so many ways. My opinion. Kill me', '2023-01-30 10:08:49', '2023-01-30 10:08:49'),
(40, 7, 3, 'Subaru Natski lived a very damaged life. Was sad that y boy couldn\'t attain true love in the end', '2023-01-30 10:09:23', '2023-01-30 10:09:23'),
(41, 29, 3, 'Saiki was so good in doing everything he did. I guess his smartassness came in handy in so many unimaginable ways', '2023-01-30 10:09:59', '2023-01-30 10:09:59'),
(42, 27, 3, 'When the twist finally hit me. I was so shocked mehn', '2023-01-30 10:10:28', '2023-01-30 10:10:28'),
(43, 28, 3, 'Two words\r\nSimply Amazing', '2023-01-30 10:10:49', '2023-01-30 10:10:49'),
(44, 31, 8, 'Code geas was legendary in so many ways', '2023-01-30 10:11:29', '2023-01-30 10:11:29'),
(45, 30, 8, 'Steins gate\'s monsters are the best in anime history', '2023-01-30 10:11:59', '2023-01-30 10:11:59'),
(46, 32, 8, 'Made in Abyss is so great in the way it engages the viewer to build a world picture of the abyss as the two protagonists scale it down', '2023-01-30 10:12:40', '2023-01-30 10:12:40'),
(47, 29, 8, 'Saiki was nice in the voice acting department', '2023-01-30 10:13:20', '2023-01-30 10:13:20');

